data.description: Welcome home to this popular Lafayette floor plan in desirable Sawmill of Greenfield! This home features an open floor plan, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths with a den or office. You will love the tall 9ft ceilings, beautiful 42 inch kitchen cabinets and gorgeous luxury vinyl plank flooring! The master retreat features double sinks, shower and walk-in closet. Neighborhood features include pool, park, and walking trails! Close to everything beautiful downtown Greenfield has to offer!
